org.activebpel.rt.bpel.coord
Interface IAeProtocolMessage

All Known Subinterfaces:
IAeSpProtocolMessage
All Known Implementing Classes:
AeProtocolMessage, AeSpProtocolMessage
public interface IAeProtocolMessage

Interface for a WS-Coordination protocol message that is exchanged between the coordinator and the participant. Note: This is an internal implementation tailored to be used with requirement 111.
